<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190956>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Caligus dakari van Beneden, 1892 male. A. genital complex and abdomen, ventral view; B. antenna, postantennal process (pap) and maxillule (mxl) in situ, ventral view; C. maxilliped; D. sternal furca in situ; E. second exopodal segment of leg 1 showing distal armature; F. leg 4. Scale-bars: A = 500 μm, B, C, D, F = 250 μm, E = 100 μm." ;
